data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful gem, recently showcased on HGTV's House Hunters for under $220,000!! This spacious 5 bedroom, 2 full bathroom nestled in such a cute neighborhood, boasts modern upgrades, including stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, newer floors and newer carpet in the bedrooms! This home having 5 bedrooms makes for multiple options for the whole family to spread out and enjoy. Plus, the fenced-in yard provides privacy and security, along with your concrete patio area making it perfect for outdoor gatherings and playtime. Don't miss out on the chance to make this stunning property your new home sweet home! Book your showing today, this home will not last long!
